HEADWORD: Rampancy
<hw>Ramp"an*cy</hw> <pr>(r⟦acr⟧mp"⟦ait⟧n*s⟦ycr⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<def>The quality or state of being rampant; excessive action or
development; exuberance; extravagance.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧They are come to
this height and <xex>rampancy</xex> of vice.⟦rdquo⟧
